Package car.tp1.ftp

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CmdControleur
    Class CmdControleur : This class receives messages from class FtpRequest and will start the methods (of class Cmds) according to the message ( = command) received by FtpRequest
    Cmds
    Class Cmds Contains all methods to process commands received (Methods are launched from Class CmdControleur)
    CodeCmd
    Class CodeCmd Contains all of commands accepts by the server
    FtpRequest
    Class FtpRequest Process an FTP Session This class receives messages received by the server and will process them.
    Param
    Class Param Contains the parameters of the ftp server You can easily edit them !
    ServerMessage
    Class ServerMessage Contains all of the code and messages of the server This code and message will be send to the client
    Serveur
    Class Serveur This class is the main class of the Server FTP implemented.
    Users
    Class Users Represents a client of the server
